    <string name="coachmark_subway_transfer_tip_title">Transferring can be faster</string>
    <string name="coachmark_subway_transfer_tip_desc">Trains running 한대앞–인천 directly come about every 30 min, while trains shuttling 한대앞–오이도 and 오이도–인천 come every 7–15 min, so transferring at 오이도 can be faster.</string>
